---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/layout/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/layout/Footer.astro';

const lang = 'en';
const title = 'Privacy Policy | SAUWA';
const description = 'Privacy policy and data protection of SAUWA (PCR Europe, S.L.). Information on the processing of personal data in accordance with the GDPR.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} lang={lang}>
  <Navbar locale={lang} />
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="update-date"><em>Last updated: October 5, 2025</em></p>

      <section>
        <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
        <p>In accordance with Regulation (EU) 2016/679 (GDPR) and Organic Law 3/2018, of December 5, on the Protection of Personal Data and guarantee of digital rights, you are hereby informed that the data controller for the personal data collected through this website is:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Legal name:</strong> PCR Europe, S.L.</li>
          <li><strong>Trade name:</strong> SAUWA</li>
          <li><strong>NIF (Tax ID):</strong> B84604461</li>
          <li><strong>Registered office:</strong> C/ Flor de los Tilos, 58 - Valdemorillo (Madrid), Spain</li>
          <li><strong>Contact email address:</strong> info@sauwa.com</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Purposes of the processing</h2>
        <p>The personal data provided by the user through this website will be processed for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Management of ticket sales and reservations:</strong> To process the purchase, payment, and reservation of access to our sauna facilities.</li>
          <li><strong>Management of inquiries and requests:</strong> To respond to inquiries, information requests, or any other requests made by users through the contact channels.</li>
          <li><strong>Sending commercial communications (Newsletter):</strong> To send newsletters, promotions, and other communications related to SAUWA's services, provided that the user has given their explicit consent by checking the corresponding box.</li>
          <li><strong>Administrative and accounting management:</strong> To carry out the administrative, billing, and accounting tasks arising from the provision of our services.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. Legal basis for the processing</h2>
        <p>The legal basis for the processing of your personal data is:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Performance of a contract:</strong> For the management of ticket purchases and reservations and the provision of the requested services.</li>
          <li><strong>Consent of the data subject:</strong> For sending commercial communications (newsletter) and for managing inquiries not linked to a contracted service.</li>
          <li><strong>Compliance with legal obligations:</strong> For the administrative, tax, and accounting procedures required by law.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. User rights</h2>
        <p>To exercise these rights, the user can send a written request, accompanied by a copy of their identity document, to the email address: info@sauwa.com</p>
        <p>Likewise, if you consider that your rights have been violated, you can file a complaint with the <strong>Spanish Data Protection Agency (AEPD)</strong>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer locale={lang} />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page { min-height: 100vh; padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem; background: var(--color-white); font-family: var(--font-avenir); }
  .legal-container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--font-canela); font-size: 3rem; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .update-date { color: var(--color-gray); margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  section { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  h2 { font-family: var(--font-avenir); font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 500; }
  p { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text); }
  ul { margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page { padding: 6rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>
